						               													<description>Aim: be the first to build your vehicle with the puzzle cards.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Rules of the game:&amp;#10;Each player chooses 2 vehicle cards and has to win all 6 puzzle cards needed to build one of the vehicles. The vehicle cards stay in front of the players during the game.&amp;#10;All the puzzle cards are dealt out to the players.&amp;#10;The players put their cards face down in a stack in front of them.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;BataPuzzle&amp;#10;The players all turn over their top card at the same time. The player whose card has the highest number wins the hand and takes from it any cards that can be used to build his chosen vehicles.&amp;#10;If two or more cards have the highest number, the winner is decided by a round of War: the players each place another card face up on top of their stack, and the player with the highest card wins all the cards in the hand.&amp;#10;The winner is the first player to complete one of his puzzles. A player can also win a two-player game by taking all of his opponent&amp;rsquo;s cards.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
